defaultThe Committee will be aware that Looked After Children (LAC) are disproportionately represented within the youth justice system. Less than 1% of all children i
defaultn England and Wales are looked after at any one time, yet up to one half of all children held in young offenders institutions are, or have previously been, looked after. 
